<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Refrain" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Refrain,</orth> to forbear, to abstain: <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.165" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 165</bibl>. With <cit><quote>from:</quote> <bibl n="shak. pp 388" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 388</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. jn 2.525" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 525</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.1.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 1, 99</bibl>. Transitively: <cit><quote>scarce I can r. the execution of my big-swoln heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.110" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 110</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>